item.title: By: Ben

item.description: That's so great to hear Ramon! I'm honored to help spark your interest again! Best of luck on your training and let me know if you ever need a second opinion as your designing it! In fact, I would love to hear what you're doing in order to see if there is anything I can do to improve my own!

item.title: By: Ramon Mercado
item.dc:creator: Ramon Mercado
item.description: Ben, I must say that you've inspired me to take the mantle yet again and start learning and playing. Starting next month I'll start my own training regiment, with the goal of getting to 1Dan for next yeas Go Congress!
